{"about_the_game":"<i>Newly rebooted for a better mind-bending experience.</i><br><br><i>Cubes</i> is a puzzle game that can only comfortably exist in virtual reality. Incorporating a mix of spatial reasoning and logic, <i>Cubes</i> presents a series of multidimensional puzzles using sets of mysterious, floating cubes. You must interact with the cubes and create patterns to fulfill each puzzle and progress.<br><br>A thoughtful, room-scale VR experience, using the space and motion of virtual reality to pit you against a new kind of puzzle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenge yourself in dozens of intriguing VR puzzles.<br></li><li>Think in multiple dimensions to meet the requirements of each puzzle.<br></li><li>Take on more advanced challenges by applying color to cubes.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Controls:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Interact - Touch objects (usually cubes) with your cursor. Pull the trigger to interact.<br></li><li>Movement - Every level exists within a self-contained, room-scale space. Simply walk around to view the puzzle from different angles.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Supported Controllers</h2>Vive hand controllers only.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/786110/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1547217191","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/786110/page.bg.jpg?t=1547217191","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/786110/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1547217191","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/786110/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1547217191","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Only","id":54},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<i>Newly rebooted for a better mind-bending experie